    dc:description "Figures 49 - 53. Armascirus key illustrations. 49 - 51 Dorsal idiosoma 49 a-e Hysterosomal shield complemented with setae 50 a-d Hysterosomal shield small, not complemented with setae 51 a-c Hysterosomal shield absent 52 a, b Pedipalp tibiotarsal claw 52 a Single claw 52 b Bifid claw 53 a Hysterosomal plate concave on lateral edges 53 b Hysterosomal plate not concave on lateral edges." ;
